{"tid":1847051,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"基因改造病毒 + 實驗室洩漏事故","createTime":"2020-01-28T00:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T10:00:18.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a65ffd6e965a2d83354d602c53668df09c44f106","tid":1847051,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T00:49:42.000Z","msg":"原來基因改造病毒早於1974年已經研發成功<br />\n<br />\n武漢又有國家級微生物實驗室<br />\n<br />\n好似好多人都懷疑今次唔係天災，而係人禍"},{"pid":"e6b94c17800853ecfda0399586bc62f17d2a2a53","tid":1847051,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:34:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>基因改造病毒相關研究</strong><br />\n<br />\n病毒爆破癌細胞<br />\n<br />\n經過人工改造，專門對付癌細胞的病毒，就像神奇的武器一般，可治療某些癌症，這些病毒軍團還能召喚免疫細胞共同消滅癌細胞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://sa.ylib.com/MagArticle.aspx?Unit=featurearticles&amp;id=2609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsa.ylib.com%2FMagArticle.aspx%3FUnit%3Dfeaturearticles%26id%3D2609&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=e7906b0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sa.ylib.com/MagArticle.aspx?Unit=featurearticles&amp;id=2609</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本病毒抗癌研究有新突破<br />\n<br />\n病毒療法採用基因改造技術，向人體內注入改造為破壞癌細胞、只感染周邊癌細胞的病毒。以往的方法是僅注入這種病毒，但還需要進一步降低副作用，增強效果。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/scienceatechnology/35812-2019-06-06-05-00-20.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.cn.nikkei.com%2Findustry%2Fscienceatechnology%2F35812-2019-06-06-05-00-20.html&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=1a8db4b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/scienceatechnology/35812-2019-06-06-05-00-20.html</a>"},{"pid":"dd410575aaf1e4e41afb57fe3b0d448c2bce865c","tid":1847051,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"基本上已可斷言武漢肺炎係來自武漢P4實驗室<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846058</a>"},{"pid":"391f818f143bb7780a7ba8a7504550f2537ccbce","tid":1847051,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"基因改造病毒，<br />\n早在1974年已經出現，<br />\n現在實驗研究緊如火如荼，<br />\n基改病毒好有用，<br />\n可以用來醫癌病和很多頑疾。<br />\n<br />\n今次武漢肺炎事件，絕對唔排除係因為基改病毒洩漏。"}]}